messages.message:
I noticed a bit of an unexpected behavior in Build.  While waiting for the UI to save a field that you're closing out of, if you happen to click again (either out of impatience or questioning whether you originally clicked on it yet), that click carries through to invisible elements behind the visible panel.

https://instabase.zoom.us/clips/share/ZyBZXNujyqjFuW36JX7S_QSbqbF77wdULWwTU1uJEj05l4QC8-LS2TflyOEqnMfbuq8ZLj450n17GNLzePZ8Q2np.Dyf5BDFvw5JbT82G
Passcode: ?H3*04Bc
this is definitely not expected! @CJ is currently working on some performance improvements for projects like yours that have many fields, so hopefully these concerns should be addressed soon!
